betsy.grammar

Enum StructureTag

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<StructureTag>
      • betsy.grammar.StructureTag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<StructureTag>

    public enum StructureTag
extends java.lang.Enum<StructureTag>
    Trees of StructureTags are used to describe a sentence. StructureTags are used to "tag" either individual words or phrases in a sentence. The tag describes the word or phrase's role in the sentence. There are clearly defined rules for what tags mean and what other tags they are allowed to contain.

    jacob
